race.comment: BUCKLE UP ARIA (1) settled off the lead and overcame a check to hit the front turning, before fading to finish sixth (16.79) in a Grade 3/4 at this track. Can find winning form here. RAGING RAMBO (8) turned in a plain effort last time when seventh at Hobart over 340m behind Aston Teresa (20.27) in a Grade 5. Key player if finds best. WINEMAKER (6) drew an outside box and was game in defeat when only 1.75 lengths from the winner Cadia Gold in second(16.22) at this track. Ready to find winning form. MYALL CLYDE (7) should be thereabouts.
